459
00:27:52,410 --> 00:27:53,735
<b>It's all for you.</b>

460
00:27:58,280 --> 00:27:59,745
<b>But...</b>

461
00:28:00,750 --> 00:28:02,975
<b>Someone is trying to get in the way.</b>

