469
00:28:28,510 --> 00:28:30,605
<b>Wait, stop. There.</b>

470
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:32,809
<b>Bring the one outside as well.</b>

471
00:28:32,810 --> 00:28:35,675
<b>Gosh, I'm out of water. Let's go, Seol-a.</b>

472
00:28:48,530 --> 00:28:51,869
