473
00:28:51,870 --> 00:28:53,165
<b>I don't know.</b>

474
00:28:53,800 --> 00:28:55,365
<b>Let's just keep trying.</b>

475
00:28:56,000 --> 00:28:57,195
<b>Come on.</b>

