480
00:29:15,490 --> 00:29:18,855
<b>Of course. You know it well.</b>

481
00:29:19,090 --> 00:29:20,025
<b>[ Goodness. ]</b>

482
00:29:21,290 --> 00:29:22,359
<b>Is that a mandarin fish?</b>

483
00:29:22,360 --> 00:29:24,925
