- Okay.</b>

533
00:32:18,070 --> 00:32:19,505
<b>You take these.</b>

534
00:32:21,610 --> 00:32:22,835
<b>Let's go.</b>

535
00:32:25,610 --> 00:32:27,945
<b>What are you doing? Follow me.</b>

536
00:32:29,180 --> 00:32:32,115
<b>What's with her? Is she a thief?</b>

537
00:32:37,190 --> 00:32:38,655
<b>Hey!</b>

538
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:47,365
<b>Gosh, those two guys made things easier.</b>

539
00:32:50,470 --> 00:32:54,705
<b>What are you going to do with all this?</b>

540
00:32:54,840 --> 00:32:58,545
<b>[ I have no clue. Gosh. ]</b>

541
00:32:58,680 --> 00:33:01,819
<b>Do you even know how to use that?</b>

