00:33:01,820 --> 00:33:03,975
<b>[ - By the looks of it, ]
- Yes.</b>

543
00:33:04,250 --> 00:33:05,689
<b>I think she does.</b>

544
00:33:05,690 --> 00:33:06,815
<b>What?</b>

545
00:33:06,850 --> 00:33:08,655
<b>I think she knows how to use it very well.</b>

546
00:33:08,914 --> 00:33:10,112
<b>Bingo.</b>

547
00:33:10,113 --> 00:33:12,559
<b>Bingo. Of course you do.</b>

548
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:14,855
<b>All right. You guys take care.</b>

549
00:33:18,130 --> 00:33:20,925
<b>Then I'll bring this back.
You guys can walk...</b>

550
00:33:25,210 --> 00:33:26,365
<b>All right.</b>

551
00:33:27,210 --> 00:33:29,705
<b>Let's go. Okay.</b>

552
00:33:30,780 --> 00:33:31,945
<b>[ I'm going. ]</b>

553
00:33:38,990 --> 00:33:41,619
<b>Painter! Try harder!</b>

