00:40:37,470 --> 00:40:40,009
<b>[ - Is this why? ]
- Mother, what do you mean?</b>

579
00:40:40,010 --> 00:40:42,375
<b>This is your dream that you want to make
come true for him?</b>

580
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:44,409
<b>- Sorry?
- Your dream was to get in the way</b>

581
00:40:44,410 --> 00:40:47,405
<b>of Donghan International's
clothing industrial complex?</b>

582
00:40:48,610 --> 00:40:49,745
<b>Mother,</b>

583
00:40:50,250 --> 00:40:52,785
<b>- I don't know what you've heard from...
