584
00:40:53,290 --> 00:40:55,585
<b>I know you don't like Chul-yong,</b>

585
00:40:55,620 --> 00:40:57,215
<b>[ but I cannot accept you affecting ]</b>

586
00:40:57,290 --> 00:40:59,985
<b>the company due to your personal feelings,</b>

587
00:41:00,130 --> 00:41:02,995
<b>both as your mother
and as an entrepreneur.</b>

588
00:41:04,200 --> 00:41:06,165
<b>- I...
- Don't do it!</b>

589
00:41:07,300 --> 00:41:09,939
<b>Don't get in the way of establishing
the clothing industrial complex.</b>

590
00:41:09,940 --> 00:41:12,439
<b>Mother, please. Just hear me out.</b>

591
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:13,535
<b>[ No. ]</b>

592
00:41:14,170 --> 00:41:15,435
<b>You listen to me.</b>

593
00:41:16,010 --> 00:41:17,205
<b>Or else,</b>

594
00:41:18,210 --> 00:41:20,675
<b>I'll have no other option
but to kick you out.</b>

595
00:42:15,870 --> 00:42:17,435
<b>To make...</b>

