605
00:44:24,600 --> 00:44:26,295
<b>Okay, let's get started.</b>

606
00:44:26,400 --> 00:44:29,495
<b>Byeol-na, you made all of this
by yourself?</b>

607
00:44:30,370 --> 00:44:31,595
<b>[ My goodness. ]</b>

608
00:44:31,600 --> 00:44:34,705
<b>I used to be a seamstress
